properties.name: length
properties.description: The number of objects in the collection.

methods.name: count
methods.description: Displays the number of elements in the AutoCorrectTable.

methods.name: item
methods.description: Returns the AutoCorrectTable with the specified index or name.

parameters.name: index
parameters.description: The index or name. Can accept: Long Integer or String.

methods.name: itemByName
methods.description: Returns the AutoCorrectTable with the specified name.

methods.name: itemByRange
methods.description: Returns the AutoCorrectTables within the specified range.

parameters.name: from
parameters.description: The AutoCorrectTable, index, or name at the beginning of the range. Can accept: AutoCorrectTable, Long Integer or String.

parameters.name: to
parameters.description: The AutoCorrectTable, index, or name at the end of the range. Can accept: AutoCorrectTable, Long Integer or String.

methods.name: firstItem
methods.description: Returns the first AutoCorrectTable in the collection.

methods.name: lastItem
methods.description: Returns the last AutoCorrectTable in the collection.

methods.name: middleItem
methods.description: Returns the middle AutoCorrectTable in the collection.

methods.name: previousItem
methods.description: Returns the AutoCorrectTable with the index previous to the specified index.

parameters.name: obj
parameters.description: The index of the AutoCorrectTable that follows the desired AutoCorrectTable.

methods.name: nextItem
methods.description: Returns the AutoCorrectTable whose index follows the specified AutoCorrectTable in the collection.

parameters.name: obj
parameters.description: The AutoCorrectTable whose index comes before the desired AutoCorrectTable.

methods.name: anyItem
methods.description: Returns any AutoCorrectTable in the collection.

methods.name: everyItem
methods.description: Returns every AutoCorrectTable in the collection.
